title: How to Stop Holding Yourself Back
itunes:title: How to Stop Holding Yourself Back
description:
Success is simple - you can either make excuses or you can create the life you want. There are no other options. In this episode, I am going to teach you how to stop making all of the excuses that are holding you back from taking the action that you need to create the life you want.
